Lolly Joe (c) Peter Valencia

Release 20/08/2016

Protection: Steam
Game Size: 1 DISC

[RELEASE NOTES]

A dog's journey to reunite with his best friend. Lolly Joe is a
3D-platforming adventure that takes you through the surreal
worlds inside a boy's subconscious mind. With his magic
lollipop, Joe must overcome a variety of challenges crafted from
his friend's dreams and memories
